reviews.text: Lovely clean beach, few arcades, fantastic chippy on the pier. A bit limited for things to entertain kids.
Lovely weather and nice beach. Lot of eating options nearby. Best thing was that the train station is right next to the beach. Very convenient for out of station travelers.
At Cleepthores it is a Wonderful sea to see also  there is the train station what Needs more Trains Running every 20 minutes.
